10
00:01:08,270 --> 00:01:11,350
And then it goes about searching for that knowledge. The second point to

11
00:01:11,350 --> 00:01:15,590
note here is, depending on the background knowledge available, the agent will

12
00:01:15,590 --> 00:01:19,500
opportunistically build the right kind of causal proofs. So if the agent knows

13
